@startuml
actor "DASH client" as DASH_client
participant "License proxy" as License_proxy
participant "License server" as License_server

DASH_client -> License_proxy: Get license
License_proxy -> License_proxy: Check if user is authorized
License_proxy -> License_server: Get license\n(Proprietary proof of authorization attached)
License_server -> License_proxy: License
License_proxy -> DASH_client: License
@enduml